       throws TransformationException
        distribute an instance, its contained sub-instances and the referenced classifiers to a certain target node
        Parameters:
        copier - lazy copier from intermediate to target model
        gatherConfigData - an implementation that is able to gather configuration data (e.g. information about dependencies to external libraries) that will be used for project configuration
        node - the instance specification of the target node
        nodeIndex - the index of the target node (used for bootloader generation)
        numberOfNodes - the total number of indexes (used for bootloader generation)
        Throws:
        TransformationException
